<ul>
<li><a href="../Robert_N._Bellah" title="Robert N. Bellah" class="mw-redirect">Bellah, Robert N.</a> (ed.) (1973). <i>Emile Durkheim: On Morality and Society, Selected Writings</i>. Chicago: The University of Chicago Press (<a href="Special_BookSources/9780226173368" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 978-0-226-17336-8</a>).</li>
