<li><a href="Roger_Cotterrell" title="Roger Cotterrell">Cotterrell, Roger</a> (ed.) (2010). <i>Emile Durkheim: Justice, Morality and Politics.</i> Ashgate (<a href="Special_BookSources/9780754627111" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 978-0-7546-2711-1</a>).</li>
