<li>Pickering, W. S. F. (ed.) (1979). <i>Durkheim: Essays on Morals and Education</i>, Routledge &amp; Kegan Paul (<a href="Special_BookSources/0710003218" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 0-7100-0321-8</a>).</li>
