<li>Tekiner, Deniz (2002). "German Idealist Foundations of Durkheim's Sociology and Teleology of Knowledge", <i>Theory and Science</i>, III, 1, <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://theoryandscience.icaap.org/content/vol003.001/tekiner.html">Online publication</a>.</li>
